{Speech 2}{}{You! What do you want to do to the, formerly, Great Ananias now?@@Get away from me!@@Go ruin someone else's business.@@Take it out on someone else.@@You've already done your worst to me.@@Just go away, you've done enough harm to me.}
{Speech 3}{}{Hello, welcome, salutations! I am the Great Ananias [He offers you a slight bow, with a flourish] I used to be in museum business before, but since then I slightly changed my specialization in accordance to the modern demands and now provide our local population with some... erm... UNCOMMON services.}
{Speech 3 Answer 5}{}{So, what kind of services do you offer, the Mighty Anana... what is your name again?}
{Speech 3 Answer 10}{}{So, what kind of services do you offer, the Mighty Anana... what is your name again?}
{Speech 3 Answer 6}{}{I'm sorry, but I'm not interested.}
{Speech 4}{}{Did you come back to enjoy the services of the Great Ananias one more time?}
{Speech 4 Answer 5}{}{So, what's your business?}
{Speech 4 Answer 10}{}{So, what's your business?}
{Speech 4 Answer 9}{}{About the doll... Will this one do? [You show the sex doll to the Great Ananias]}
{Speech 4 Answer 9*}{}{About the doll... Will this one do? [You show the sex doll to the Great Ananias]}
{Speech 4 Answer 11}{}{I'd like to use your services.}
{Speech 4 Answer 8}{}{I'd like to use your services.}
{Speech 4 Answer 6}{}{I think I don't need any services today. Farewell.}
{Speech 5}{}{To be honest, I'm still only looking for such an opportunity. And perhaps it's YOU who can help me.}
{Speech 5 Answer 7}{}{Me? How can I help you?}
{Speech 5 Answer 6}{}{I'm not interested at all.}
{Speech 6}{}{The Great Ananias is always glad to have clients!@@It seems to me that you liked it and I'll see you again some day.}
{Speech 7}{}{Well, if you could find a new rubber doll somewhere, I would gladly buy it from you.}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Sounds interesting, I'll give it a try.}
{Speech 7 Answer 6}{}{To heck with you and your dolls, I'm not a kid to play with them!}
{Speech 8}{}{We've had a lot of clients lately and... well, we need to replace some of our equipment. So if you could find a new rubber doll somewhere, I would gladly buy it from you. Deal?}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Perhaps I'll do as you said if I find it.}
{Speech 8 Answer 6}{}{I'm not interested at all.}
{Speech 9}{}{Splendid! Here's your money.}
{Speech 10}{}{I definitely need some help, but I don't think you're the person who can help me.}
{Speech 11}{}{The prices of the Great Ananias are the best in the whole Wasteland. Only 10 dollars for a session of the hottest and purest love!}
{Speech 11 Answer 13}{}{Hey, I like it! Here's the money.}
{Speech 11 Answer 6}{}{I think I don't have enough money. I guess I'll be back when I get enough.}
{Speech 11 Answer 6*}{}{I don't need any 'services' anymore.}
{Speech 12}{}{I'm sorry, but we don't have any suitable services for ladies.}
{Speech 13}{}{[The Great Ananias takes the money and leads you behind the curtains, where you discover a big battered doll laying on the table and spend some time one on one with it]}
{Speech 13 Answer Exit}{}{Оh yeah, yeah!@@!@@Aaaaaah!@@Yeah, baby, yeah!!!@@Oooooooh!@@Marvellous!@@Ooooooh! Just awesome!@@Oops... Ananius, I think I've torn your doll...@@Mmm... I'll be back, baby...}
{Speech 14}{}{I'm sorry, but I don't do business with imbeciles.}
